---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
import VantaDots from "../components/VantaBackground.jsx";
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="es" class="h-full">
<head>
<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<script src="/js/three.r134.min.js" is:inline></script>
<script src="/js/vanta.dots.min.js" is:inline></script>
</head>
<body class="h-full min-h-screen overflow-x-hidden">
    <VantaDots client:load />
<div class="relative min-h-screen flex flex-col">
<Header />
<main class="relative z-10 flex-1 px-6 py-8 pb-24">
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-[rgb(120,108,187,0.3)] text-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">üßë‚ÄçüöÄ Hello, Astronaut!</h1>
<p class="mb-4  leading-relaxed">
 Welcome to the official <a href="https://astro.build/" class="text-purple-600 hover:text-purple-800 underline">Astro</a> blog starter template. This
 template serves as a lightweight, minimally-styled starting point for anyone looking to build
 a personal website, blog, or portfolio with Astro.
</p>
<p class="mb-4  leading-relaxed">
 This template comes with a few integrations already configured in your
<code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">astro.config.mjs</code> file. You can customize your setup with
<a href="https://astro.build/integrations" class="text-purple-600 hover:text-purple-800 underline">Astro Integrations</a> to add tools like Tailwind,
 React, or Vue to your project.
</p>
<p class="mb-4  leading-relaxed">Here are a few ideas on how to get started with the template:</p>
<ul class="mb-6 space-y-2 ">
<li class="flex items-start">
<span class="text-purple-500 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
Edit this page in <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">src/pages/index.astro</code>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start">
<span class="text-purple-500 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
Edit the site header items in <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">src/components/Header.astro</code>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start">
<span class="text-purple-500 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
Add your name to the footer in <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">src/components/Footer.astro</code>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start">
<span class="text-purple-500 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
Check out the included blog posts in <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">src/content/blog/</code>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start">
<span class="text-purple-500 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
Customize the blog post page layout in <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">src/layouts/BlogPost.astro</code>
</li>
</ul>
<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
 Have fun! If you get stuck, remember to
<a href="https://docs.astro.build/" class="text-purple-600 hover:text-purple-800 underline">read the docs</a>
 or <a href="https://astro.build/chat" class="text-purple-600 hover:text-purple-800 underline">join us on Discord</a> to ask questions.
</p>
</div>
</main>
</div>
<Footer />
</body>
</html>